metadata.name: Defiants Indigo Chrome I
metadata.description:
Indigo Chrome Defiants©

A Fall Collection '22

Limited edition Collection of 8 1/1 The Defiants in a brand new style and unique colors.

The Defiants Collection is an unique series of 3D NFT's, create by the Defithenorm Collective. Each 1/1 collectible is minted on the Ethereum blockchain, becoming a permanent fixture until the aliens inevitably gamma-ray the world’s servers.

By joining us, you’re investing in an underground society of hackers, aliens, robots and misfits.
